The term '''"Stay-behind"''' is referred to an activity which purpose is to retrive secrets of the one ''"in front"''. Standing behind ones back, reading secrets over the shoulder, without the ones knowledge is most likely the origin. Spy and intelligence activities is known to use these methods.

A parallel can also be made to '''"Behind-enemy-lines"''' which is referred to as beeing behind the enemy without its knownledge. Did the enemy know, you wouldn't be behind their lines. The purpose of such activity could be to create a surprice attack as well as gathering information for intelligence purposes.

The word '''"Stay"''' in "Stay-behind" is guessed to refer to long time activites such as becoming a part of the ones infront but yet serv others with uncovered secrets, prior to get behind ones shoulder to retive specific secrets.

One of the most famous "Stay-behind" operation is: '''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gladio Operation Gladio]''' which was sponsored by NATO and CIA during the Cold War.